aa(lp26
VFortunately for me, though, I've got two great kids
p27
aVwho are still curious about the world.
p28
aVSebastian \u2014 he's still curious about the world, and in 2014, in spring,
p29
aVhe brought in a ground beetle from the garden.
p30
aVThere was nothing particularly special about this insect \u2014
p31
aVyou know, it was a common species.
p32
aVBut he was still curious,
p33
aVand he brought it up to my office,
p34
aVand we decided to look at it under his microscope.
p35
aVHe had a little science kit for Christmas.
p36
aVAnd this is what we saw.
