aa(lp38
VNow, when I first saw this, it blew me away.
p39
aVUp here \u2014 this is the back of the ground beetle.
p40
aVWhen I first saw it, it reminded me of a galaxy.
p41
aVAnd all the time, this had just been outside our window.
p42
aVYou know, I was looking for this extraordinary subject,
p43
aVand it took Seb's eyes and curiosity to bring it in to me.
